    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, making it an ideal choice for a daily driver where utility matters more than aesthetics. The exterior has several visible scratches, a few minor door dings, and some fading on the trim pieces consistent with its age. Inside, the upholstery shows signs of regular use with some wear on the driver's seat and minor staining on the carpets, though all electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and runs well, though a prospective buyer should expect upcoming routine maintenance items. This is a solid, honest vehicle for someone seeking dependable transportation at a reasonable price point.",
