    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs great and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for many more adventures with you. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I think you\u2019ll really enjoy how it handles on the road. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and help you get behind the wheel of this beauty!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
