      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is robust, utilizing a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive valve lash adjustment. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded bushings, providing communicative feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering. A mechanically honest specimen for the purist looking for peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
